":573524,"uid":83060,"like":39,"dislike":7,"score":32,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-26T18:03:00.000Z","msg":"法國人破壞佢啲單車係由於不耻佢公司假借共享之名去霸地賺錢，係政治正確，唔好同港豚混為一談。"},{"pid":"3bc81e53d95cc13a091600cd686fca85162027e1","tid":573524,"uid":25643,"like":51,"dislike":3,"score":48,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-02-26T18:07:18.000Z","msg":"寧願踩GoBee 都唔要大陸 ofo <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"953dc0ab04b594fc4631f9a8b807916c590182b7","tid":573524,"uid":16676,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-26T18:19:21.000Z","msg":"GoBee 條款寫住話唔退儲值額<br />\nDeposit 可以退<br />\n<br />\n咁當然唔買儲值額啦, 唔用果時無得退, 焗住要用晒佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0e9dc9e4e63429d088ef9b2591dd1cbbee93011","tid":573524,"uid":16676,"like":4,"dislike":26,"score":-22,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-26T18:23:07.000Z","msg":"ofo 可以逐次用信用咕扣數(找數) <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/yipes10.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n雖然好多時都唔使錢(free) <br />\n起碼唔會比左舊錢出黎驚退唔返 <br />\n<br />\n試過一次: 儲值果度一襟入去就比左錢, 唔使pwd, 入左錢入去儲值 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/yipes100.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/yipes100.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/yipes100.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n之後打上CS, ofo 都可以過返條數比我<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/agree2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b0d5bc7aa457577ad0f70419f85aee5964e556b","tid":573524,"uid":26389,"like":6,"dislike":62,"score":-56,"quote":{"pid":"3bc81e53d95cc13a091600cd686fca85162027e1","tid":573524,"uid":25643,"like":51,"dislike":3,"score":48,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-02-26T18:07:18.000Z","msg":"寧願踩GoBee 都唔要大陸 ofo <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-02-26T18:23:23.000Z","msg":"但係ofo優惠真心多 我用左大半年gobee得果15$優惠咁大把<br />\n而且成日lock/unlock唔到搞到扣錢<br />\n依家ofo個免費優惠做到4月 而且車多"},{"pid":"2d828c6ef9d363a7e1c23f1ff9350a2dab15d422","tid":573524,"